    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sidereal Dominion: Avalon is an indie strategy game where you command an interstellar empire, controlling its expansion through the galaxy and directly controlling your fleets in real-time space battles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on a map of the Milky Way and directly command your fleets in real-time battles .</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play premade governments, or make your own custom colony by mixing traits and making a flag.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with three different victory conditions. Reclaim Earth, or terraform a new homeworld for humanity .</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with a simulated economy that automatically adjusts production of goods. Micromanage your population as much or as little as you want .</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build mines and monopolize resources to obtain bonuses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift your government’s structure on a political chart, unlocking different mechanics to use.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game always starts the same but adds procedural elements as time goes on.</p></li></ul>",
